trailingComments.value:
*
 * Set a block of a matrix 
 * 
 * @param {Array} x
 * @param {Array} from
 * @param {Array} to
 * @param {Array} B
 * @returns {Array}
 * @example
 * 
 * setBlock([[1,2,3], [3,4,5]], [0,0], [1,1],[[2,2],[2,2]])
 * // [[2,2,3],[2,2,5]]
